WEBVTT

1
00:35:01.360 --> 00:35:04.210 
和其他人分享价值观的地方
protected by that American flag.

2
00:35:04.300 --> 00:35:09.500 
同样地 两侧建有拱门的麦当劳
It could be said that beautiful building flanked by those arches

3
00:35:09.570 --> 00:35:12.050 
或多或少有着同样的价值和意义
signifies more or less the same thing.

4
00:35:12.140 --> 00:35:16.470 
店内不仅有美味的汉堡
It doesn't just say delicious hamburgers inside.

5
00:35:16.540 --> 00:35:19.060 
还代表着家庭 代表着社会群体
They signify family. It signifies community.

6
00:35:19.150 --> 00:35:21.770 
这是美国人聚在一起共同进餐的地方
It's a place where American's come together to break bread.

7
00:35:21.850 --> 00:35:25.710 
我正式告诉你们
I am telling you,

8
00:35:25.790 --> 00:35:30.630 
麦当劳可以成为新时代的美国教堂
McDonald's can be the new American church.

9
00:35:32.390 --> 00:35:34.180 
满足人类的肉体和灵魂
Feeding bodies and feeding souls

